1
00:01:06,720 --> 00:01:07,320
Wait.

2
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:09,370
There are footprints here.

3
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,160
This size...

4
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:15,880
must be a child's footprint.

5
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,170
Who is it?

6
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:34,120
Don't run!

7
00:01:36,160 --> 00:01:36,640
Stop!

8
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:38,360
Stop!

9
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:51,450
Why is it you?

10
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:53,600
Come here.

11
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:01,530
Why are you here?

12
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:04,560
I met a human trafficker.

13
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:05,840
He told me

14
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,240
this ruined temple used to be

15
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:08,840
their regular trading spot.

16
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:10,280
So I came to take a look.

17
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,440
But he ran too fast,

18
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:13,640
so I couldn't catch him.

19
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:15,360
He vanished in the blink of an eye.

20
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:17,620
Did you see what that person looked like?

21
00:02:18,079 --> 00:02:19,280
He was wearing a mask,

22
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:21,720
so I didn't see his face clearly.

23
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,440
But I saw

24
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:26,320
a scar on that person's hand.

25
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:27,320
On the right hand.

26
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:28,320
It was quite long.

27
00:02:35,079 --> 00:02:36,280
Russian cigarettes.

28
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,400
Imported.

29
00:02:47,079 --> 00:02:48,140
What are you doing?

30
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:52,570
Brother Bao.

31
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,160
I saw today that

32
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:56,579
Gu Dachuan also has a scar on his hand.

33
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,240
Are you saying

34
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:04,240
the trafficker might be Gu Dachuan?

35
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:07,680
I just think

36
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,850
it's too much of a coincidence.

37
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:23,440
I don't recognize him.

38
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:24,800
Did you look carefully?

39
00:03:25,079 --> 00:03:26,740
I really don't recognize him.

40
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,520
I'm not a police officer.

41
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:30,930
How can I identify people just by looking?

42
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,560
Let me tell you,

43
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:35,329
withholding information adds to your crime.

44
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:37,440
Officer.

45
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:39,040
I'm already in here.

46
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:40,770
How would I dare hide anything?

47
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,640
I am looking.

48
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:47,400
Wait.

49
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:49,320
Th-This person looks familiar.

50
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:50,450
Do you remember now?

51
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,640
Isn't this Brother Long?

52
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:57,120
Long.

53
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:58,400
Who is Long?

54
00:03:59,480 --> 00:04:01,520
He used to buy medicine at my shop.

55
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:03,370
People called him Long.

56
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:06,240
Later, when the Guimu Group was destroyed,

57
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,880
he never came back.

58
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:17,529
Gu Dachuan was a member of the Guimu Group.

59
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:21,440
That's just the drug dealer's side of the story.

60
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:22,720
We can't be sure yet.

61
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:25,480
Look.

62
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:28,760
In the data Leng Fang provided earlier,

63
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,280
there is also a person named Long.

64
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:32,210
If her investigation is accurate,

65
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,730
Gu Dachuan is very likely Long.

66
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:37,560
Then Gu Dachuan kidnapping his own son

67
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,730
doesn't make sense.

68
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:42,200
If Gu Dachuan is really part of the Ghost Mother Group,

69
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:44,060
then he must have a lot of enemies.

70
00:04:44,080 --> 00:04:46,680
Maybe someone kidnapped Gu Yitong for revenge.

71
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:49,010
Gu Dachuan is with the Ghost Mother Group,

72
00:04:49,320 --> 00:04:51,380
and Leng Fang is investigating them.

73
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:54,690
Could Leng Fang have kidnapped Gu Yitong?

74
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:58,040
Theoretically, it's possible,

75
00:04:58,760 --> 00:05:01,080
but Leng Fang doesn't know Gu Dachuan.

76
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:03,880
If Leng Fang knew

77
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:05,240
that Gu Dachuan is Brother Long,

78
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:07,200
she would have said so when she reported the case.

79
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:09,440
It could also be other parents.

80
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:14,000
There were so many families victimized by the Ghost Mother Group back then.

81
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:16,930
We can't rule out that others are also investigating

82
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:18,120
and have found out

83
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:19,920
that Gu Dachuan is Brother Long.

84
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:27,120
It seems we need to look into the families

85
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:29,180
victimized by the Ghost Mother case.

86
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:49,820
Wonton.

87
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,400
Why are you following me?

88
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:05,120
I know.

89
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:08,130
You are Gu Yitong's mother.

90
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:16,640
Impossible.

91
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:19,360
Dachuan can't be a trafficker.

92
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,400
Believe it or not,

93
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:22,720
you can ask him yourself.

94
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:25,740
Even if he was a trafficker years ago,

95
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:27,120
how can you be sure

96
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,770
that he took your daughter?

97
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:31,100
If your child went missing

98
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:33,180
and you saw the kidnapper,

99
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:34,780
could you ever forget?

100
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:42,320
Shengnan.

101
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:45,120
Shengnan.

102
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:50,320
Shengnan.

103
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:52,320
So,

104
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:55,500
you kidnapped Tongtong, didn't you?

105
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:57,720
Aren't you afraid we'll go to the police?

106
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:58,980
Go ahead and report me.

107
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:01,500
Only I know where Gu Yitong is.

108
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:03,460
Whether you see him

109
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,320
is up to you.

110
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:09,920
Gu Yitong isn't your biological son,

111
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,850
but I'm surprised you care so much.

112
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:12,960
As a mother,

113
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:15,660
I think you can understand how I feel.

114
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:16,680
Don't worry.

115
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:18,920
I've made a deal with Gu Dachuan.

116
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:21,050
As long as he returns my daughter to me,

117
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:23,200
I'll return Gu Yitong to him.

118
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,130
Even if what you say is true,

119
00:07:26,640 --> 00:07:28,000
it's been eight years.

120
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,920
How could he possibly find your daughter?

121
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:32,050
That's his problem.

122
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:33,720
I have

123
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:36,210
only one condition.

124
00:07:44,400 --> 00:07:45,040
Take care.

125
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:45,760
Again.

126
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,000
Mom, you're back.

127
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:00,960
What took you so long?

128
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:14,920
What's wrong?

129
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,840
Can you still find her daughter?

130
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:25,640
How long do you plan to keep this from me?

131
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:27,740
Leng Fang told me everything.

132
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,200
What did she say?

133
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:50,160
She said as long as you return her daughter,

134
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,570
she'll let Tongtong go.

135
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:58,120
Can you find her daughter or not?

136
00:08:58,680 --> 00:09:00,010
It's been so many years.

137
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:02,210
Where am I supposed to look?

138
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,720
Didn't you sell her back then?

139
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,480
Go ask around.

140
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:05,560
We can buy her back.

141
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:06,680
No need to ask.

142
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,540
Her daughter wasn't sold.

143
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:12,120
I abandoned her.

144
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:18,000
It was chaotic everywhere that year.

145
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:20,000
I couldn't find the original buyer,

146
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:21,880
or anyone to take her.

147
00:09:22,920 --> 00:09:23,840
So I wanted

148
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,600
to get rid of her quickly.

149
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:32,520
It was the Mid-Autumn Festival.

150
00:09:32,520 --> 00:09:34,000
I felt sorry for the girl,

151
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:36,280
so I left her at a temple gate.

152
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,520
Zhongqiu.

153
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:57,880
You left her at the temple entrance.

154
00:09:59,040 --> 00:10:01,100
I went to the temple and asked around.

155
00:10:02,520 --> 00:10:03,520
No one remembers.

156
00:10:14,160 --> 00:10:15,160
What should we do?

157
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:19,880
I have a plan.

158
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,820
I want to buy another girl.

159
00:10:23,560 --> 00:10:25,080
It's been so many years anyway,

160
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:27,010
so she definitely won't remember.

161
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:30,010
Don't worry.

162
00:10:31,160 --> 00:10:33,290
I'll definitely bring Tongtong back.

163
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:42,320
Come.

164
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:47,450
How did it go?

165
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,860
They moved out a long time ago.

166
00:10:51,880 --> 00:10:53,240
This was the last one.

167
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,320
Checking like this

168
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:56,450
isn't going to work.

169
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:59,280
People with a grudge against Gu Dachuan

170
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:01,120
aren't necessarily just his victims.

171
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:01,960
Maybe

172
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:04,360
it's a member of his old Ghost Mother Group.

173
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:06,560
If it's to get revenge on Gu Dachuan,

174
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,560
then the kidnapper

175
00:11:07,560 --> 00:11:10,160
is likely using Gu Yitong as a bargaining chip.

176
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:12,660
He'll definitely contact Gu Dachuan again.

177
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,460
Let's go see him again.

178
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:23,400
Officers,

179
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:24,880
is something wrong this late?

180
00:11:24,880 --> 00:11:26,010
Where is Gu Dachuan?

181
00:11:27,160 --> 00:11:28,620
He went out for something.

182
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:29,740
Where did he go?

183
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:32,760
I don't know.

184
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:39,320
Did you know Gu Dachuan was a kidnapper?

185
00:11:47,920 --> 00:11:49,450
What are you talking about?

186
00:11:50,800 --> 00:11:51,960
We've checked.

187
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:53,970
Eight years ago, Gu Dachuan

188
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:56,920
was involved in multiple child trafficking cases.

189
00:11:56,920 --> 00:11:58,680
So Gu Yitong's kidnapping

190
00:11:59,080 --> 00:11:59,800
is likely

191
00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:00,960
an act of revenge.

192
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:05,000
This may be hard to accept,

193
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:06,800
but the priority now is

194
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:09,060
to find the person who took Gu Yitong.

195
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:13,520
But...

196
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:16,020
I really don't know anything.

197
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,720
Has Gu Dachuan met anyone recently?

198
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:31,020
When I got back from the market today,

199
00:12:31,640 --> 00:12:33,200
someone from his hometown came to see him.

200
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,260
From his hometown?

201
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:36,200
What did they talk about?

202
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,210
I don't know.

203
00:12:38,680 --> 00:12:39,720
When I got back,

204
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,330
they were just leaving.

205
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:42,920
Do you know that person?

206
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:44,120
Was it a man or a woman?

207
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:45,880
A woman.

208
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,490
But I don't know her.

209
00:12:48,160 --> 00:12:50,760
Dachuan just told me she was from his hometown.

210
00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:52,640
But after she left,

211
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,640
Dachuan seemed a bit off.

212
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:57,440
I asked him,

213
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,170
but he wouldn't tell me.

214
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:00,400
As far as you know,

215
00:13:00,680 --> 00:13:02,410
where else would Gu Dachuan go?

216
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:06,930
I really don't know.

217
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:08,720
Dachuan said

218
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:12,080
he was going to find a friend to help look for Tongtong.

219
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:16,980
Sorry to disturb you, Mrs. Gu.

220
00:13:26,440 --> 00:13:27,600
Is it possible he went to find

221
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:28,880
his old accomplices?

222
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,320
Let's go.

223
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:58,360
He hasn't been dead for long.

224
00:14:03,520 --> 00:14:04,640
The skull is fractured.

225
00:14:04,640 --> 00:14:06,770
It was likely caused by a blunt object.

226
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:11,370
The Fenglei Golden Hammer.

227
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:13,330
This is Lei Zhenzi's artifact.

228
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:14,850
Why did it fall here?

229
00:14:23,800 --> 00:14:25,280
There are scratches on the victim's forearm.

230
00:14:25,280 --> 00:14:26,960
They must be from a struggle.

231
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:28,240
Dou Mingcong.

232
00:14:28,400 --> 00:14:29,440
Have the scene sealed off.

233
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:29,840
Yes.

234
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:42,200
It's basically confirmed

235
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:44,120
that the head wound was fatal.

236
00:14:44,480 --> 00:14:45,600
The person Gu Dachuan was looking for

237
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:47,400
is likely the one who killed him.

238
00:14:47,760 --> 00:14:48,880
Zeng Xiaoyi said

239
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:51,480
Gu Dachuan went to ask a friend for help.

240
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:53,760
What kind of friend would want to kill him?

241
00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:56,280
Gu Dachuan probably wasn't looking for a friend,

242
00:14:56,280 --> 00:14:59,000
but meeting the person who abducted Gu Yitong.

243
00:14:59,280 --> 00:15:01,600
The woman looking for him at the wonton shop today

244
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:03,880
is likely the one who abducted Gu Yitong.

245
00:15:04,280 --> 00:15:06,410
So, the kidnappers killed Gu Dachuan.

246
00:15:06,480 --> 00:15:07,480
It's very likely.

247
00:15:08,560 --> 00:15:10,560
The kidnappers probably took Gu Yitong

248
00:15:10,560 --> 00:15:11,880
to blackmail Gu Dachuan.

249
00:15:11,880 --> 00:15:13,210
But Gu Dachuan wouldn't

250
00:15:13,280 --> 00:15:15,160
or couldn't meet their demands,

251
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:17,680
so they killed him in a rage.

252
00:15:18,680 --> 00:15:19,440
That means

253
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:22,240
the murderer is hiding among

254
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:24,640
the families of the victims from back then.

255
00:15:24,760 --> 00:15:25,280
Right.

256
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:32,440
This is the cigarette butt

257
00:15:32,440 --> 00:15:34,700
I found in the ruined temple two days ago.

258
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:36,140
A fresh cigarette butt

259
00:15:36,160 --> 00:15:37,220
has high moisture.

260
00:15:37,280 --> 00:15:38,520
It should be elastic.

261
00:15:38,760 --> 00:15:39,690
But look at this.

262
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:41,340
It crumbles at a touch.

263
00:15:41,520 --> 00:15:43,120
It's at least five years old.

264
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:45,680
You mean someone

265
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:48,720
deliberately planted this old cigarette butt

266
00:15:49,360 --> 00:15:50,720
in the ruined temple?

267
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:55,060
Then the child's footprints were faked too.

268
00:15:55,160 --> 00:15:56,360
Someone is deliberately leading us

269
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:57,620
to suspect Gu Dachuan.

270
00:16:00,640 --> 00:16:01,800
Could it be...

271
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:04,960
Leng Fang?

272
00:16:17,400 --> 00:16:18,320
Inspectors.

273
00:16:20,320 --> 00:16:21,980
Is there news about Shengnan?

274
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:35,040
This.

275
00:16:35,720 --> 00:16:36,650
Have you seen it?

276
00:16:48,480 --> 00:16:50,010
You really haven't seen it?

277
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:52,800
You probably picked this up years ago,

278
00:16:53,240 --> 00:16:55,970
and planted it in the ruined temple for us to find.

279
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:58,060
You knew Gu Dachuan was Brother Long,

280
00:16:58,080 --> 00:16:58,760
didn't you?

281
00:17:00,760 --> 00:17:02,480
Did that woman tell you?

282
00:17:04,599 --> 00:17:05,160
Yes.

283
00:17:05,560 --> 00:17:07,490
She's the one who came for Dachuan.

284
00:17:10,200 --> 00:17:11,760
She's definitely not his biological mother.

285
00:17:11,760 --> 00:17:14,160
It seems she never wants to see Gu Yitong again.

286
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:15,839
So to take revenge on Gu Dachuan,

287
00:17:15,839 --> 00:17:17,170
you abducted his child.

288
00:17:17,760 --> 00:17:19,490
He abducted my daughter first.

289
00:17:20,400 --> 00:17:21,930
How did you find Gu Dachuan?

290
00:17:22,480 --> 00:17:24,160
It wasn't easy finding him.

291
00:17:25,480 --> 00:17:27,480
I knew kidnappers move around a lot.

292
00:17:28,760 --> 00:17:31,040
I didn't see his face clearly back then,

293
00:17:31,520 --> 00:17:33,920
but I saw his right hand had six fingers.

294
00:17:34,560 --> 00:17:36,890
So I became a ticket seller at the station.

295
00:17:37,600 --> 00:17:38,260
One ticket.

296
00:17:38,640 --> 00:17:39,400
To Wuxi.

297
00:17:40,840 --> 00:17:42,370
I just wanted to try my luck.

298
00:17:43,680 --> 00:17:45,740
I didn't expect to actually find him.

299
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:51,650
Tickets to Wuxi.

300
00:17:52,280 --> 00:17:52,920
Wuxi.

301
00:17:53,960 --> 00:17:54,920
Where are you going?

302
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:55,680
Are you selling tickets?

303
00:17:55,680 --> 00:17:56,810
Sell us the tickets!

304
00:17:59,520 --> 00:18:00,280
Sell the tickets!

305
00:18:00,280 --> 00:18:01,810
Give us the tickets, hurry!

306
00:18:03,160 --> 00:18:04,280
I hate myself.

307
00:18:05,880 --> 00:18:06,680
I hate myself.

308
00:18:06,680 --> 00:18:07,920
Why didn't I immediately

309
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:09,000
grab him?

310
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:12,740
I thought I'd never see him again.

311
00:18:15,760 --> 00:18:17,720
But heaven rewards the faithful.

312
00:18:18,360 --> 00:18:19,400
A few years later,

313
00:18:20,680 --> 00:18:21,760
he appeared again.

314
00:18:23,600 --> 00:18:24,160
Here.

315
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:26,400
Your wonton soup.

316
00:18:28,760 --> 00:18:29,600
Enjoy.

317
00:18:35,680 --> 00:18:36,520
Enjoy.

318
00:18:44,360 --> 00:18:45,000
Honey,

319
00:18:45,200 --> 00:18:46,730
what do you want for dinner?

320
00:18:46,840 --> 00:18:47,840
Anything is fine.

321
00:18:51,880 --> 00:18:53,440
Mom, I want something good.

322
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:54,120
Mom,

323
00:18:54,120 --> 00:18:55,840
can we have sweet and sour fish tonight?

324
00:18:55,840 --> 00:18:56,640
Tell Mom.

325
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:57,640
Sweet and sour fish.

326
00:18:57,640 --> 00:18:58,320
Okay.

327
00:18:58,400 --> 00:18:58,800
Okay.

328
00:18:58,800 --> 00:19:01,160
Mom, I want braised pork today.

329
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:02,360
Braised pork?

330
00:19:02,680 --> 00:19:03,160
Okay.

331
00:19:03,440 --> 00:19:05,160
Mom will buy meat for you tonight, okay?

332
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:05,600
Okay.

333
00:19:06,200 --> 00:19:06,920
Yay!

334
00:19:07,560 --> 00:19:09,520
Our Tongtong is growing taller.

335
00:19:10,120 --> 00:19:11,320
Let Dad cook for you.

336
00:19:11,680 --> 00:19:13,340
Dad will cook for you tonight.

337
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:14,400
Make some meat

338
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:15,680
so you grow tall.

339
00:19:16,240 --> 00:19:16,800
Okay.
